<lb/><p rend="right"><placeName>River Shire</placeName> 26<hi rend="underline"><hi rend="sup">th</hi></hi> Dec<hi rend="sup">r</hi>
<lb/>1863 </p>
<lb/><p>My Dear Tom</p>
<lb/><p>I was very 
<lb/>much concerned to hear of 
<lb/>your illness, but could 
<lb/>only commit you into the 
<lb/>gracious care &amp; keeping 
<lb/>of our merciful creator. 
<lb/><choice><reg>T</reg><orig>t</orig></choice>his you must do for 
<lb/>yourself and then it will 
<lb/>be with you in life 
<lb/>and in death. </p>
			
